data.description: Welcome to your inviting 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that boasts ample living space, including a basement apartment, perfect for multi-generational living or rental income potential. As you step inside, you're greeted by a bright atmosphere, with large windows flooding the home with natural light. All windows were replaced in 2022 to make the home more efficient. The main level features a cozy living room, ideal for gatherings with family and friends. The adjacent kitchen is equipped with ample counter space, and plenty of storage for all your culinary needs. With five well-appointed bedrooms, there's room for everyone to rest and recharge. The master suite offers a peaceful retreat. Downstairs, the fully finished basement provides even more living space. Outside, the spacious backyard is a tranquil escape, perfect for summer barbecues. Plus, with easy access to Mountain View Corridor, commuting is a breeze, while nearby shopping, restaurants, parks, schools, and churches ensure you have everything you need right at your fingertips. Don't miss your chance to make this fantastic West Valley home yours. Schedule a showing today and start living the lifestyle you've always dreamed of!
